Integrate mobile TON wallet connectivity for deposits and withdrawals

Introduce TON Connect integration for mobile wallet connectivity, including a new `TonConnectProvider` and `MobileWalletIntegration` component, enabling deposits, withdrawals, and game participation with TON cryptocurrency.

